1
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,410
Dailing.

2
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:45,330
Dailing.

3
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,000
Didn't we agree to go to the library today?

4
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,880
Why did you leave first?

5
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,880
My stomach hurts.

6
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:53,200
Then sit down for a while.

7
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:56,580
Wait for me.

8
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:57,960
Chen Angwei.

9
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:12,539
Ibuprofen.

10
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,220
These are for daytime use.

11
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,680
These are for nighttime use.

12
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,640
And just drink plenty of water.

13
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,560
How do you know so much?

14
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,440
Have you bought them for someone else?

15
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,240
No, I haven't.

16
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,600
I looked it up online.

17
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,400
The way you look right now,

18
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,680
you look like an idiot.

19
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,240
When I went to buy this stuff just now,

20
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,320
a lot of people laughed at me.

21
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,979
Of course they'd laugh at you.

22
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,340
Buying so many things,

23
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,840
like you're stocking up.

24
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,050
Well, I bought them for you.

25
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:53,680
Chen Angwei,

26
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,680
having you here

27
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,340
is really nice.

28
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,960
Let's not go to the library today.

29
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,400
I'll go to the library to copy the notes,

30
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,130
and you can copy mine tomorrow.

31
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:09,759
Can you walk?

32
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:13,530
Carry me.

33
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,200
Chen Angwei.

34
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,770
Long time no see.

35
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,600
How have you been lately?

36
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,500
How are things?

37
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,460
What about you?

38
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,120
How are you doing?

39
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:02,840
Not good.

40
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:05,720
Very bad.

41
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,660
You asked to meet me this time.

42
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,940
There must be something going on.

43
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:22,400
Danpa is teaming up with Ou Shaowen to deal with Angwei.

44
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,329
I don't want to hear about that man.

45
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,280
I know you have

46
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,880
the evidence that Danpa killed Aunt Chen Qian.

47
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,520
Can you leave it to me?

48
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,850
You know I can't betray him.

49
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,770
If it weren't for Danpa,

50
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,200
I would have died on the streets long ago.

51
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,600
I know you owe him a lot.

52
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,000
But Danpa is a demon

53
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,920
with blood on his hands.

54
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,220
Do you think just because you follow him,

55
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,320
he won't kill you one day?

56
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,370
He saved my life in the first place.

57
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:58,760
Besides,

58
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:02,420
What do the deaths of those people have to do with me?

59
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,480
Dailing.

60
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,740
You have no idea how lucky you are.

61
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,480
I'm not as lucky as you.

62
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,040
Cherish it.

63
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,640
Is there really no way

64
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,840
to help Angwei?

65
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,200
There must be.

66
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,720
How can I let you

67
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,180
bear all this by yourself?

68
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,320
Enjoy.

69
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,560
You're here.

70
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,760
After the mess at the board meeting yesterday,

71
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:56,360
I thought you wouldn't come.

72
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:57,680
Sit down.

73
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,100
Let's talk.

74
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,700
As for your words, Father,

75
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,180
I have always obeyed them,

76
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,740
and been at your disposal.

77
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,680
But now that you know

78
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,730
you're just my adopted son,

79
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,860
will you still be so obedient?

80
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,520
Even though I'm just an adopted son,

81
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,810
I remember how carefully you nurtured

82
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,840
and raised me all these years.

83
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,600
You took back the casino,

84
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:44,080
but you also let me take over the pier business.

85
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,320
It's not a loss for me.

86
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,280
I accept it.

87
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,360
Angwei.

88
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,080
What if I said

89
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,760
I want to take back

90
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,920
everything

91
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,680
you have?

92
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,960
You said it yourself.

93
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,800
You are just my adopted son.

94
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,680
And now,

95
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:14,360
Shaowen is my adopted son.

96
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,400
There is no difference between you two.

97
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,200
It's just that

98
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,880
he is much more

99
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,540
obedient than you.

100
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,960
So you never intended to make a deal with me.

101
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,720
You treat me as a pawn.

102
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,320
I won't be at your mercy.

103
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,159
Angwei,

104
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,400
you have no way out.

105
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,200
Danpa,

106
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,400
this is no fun.

107
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,000
Sit down.

108
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:10,460
Weren't you quite arrogant just now?

109
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,090
Why aren't you talking now?

110
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,040
Come on.

111
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,900
Sign the contract.

112
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,340
What are you doing?

113
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,100
Godfather.

114
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,570
He has signed the contract.

115
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,960
Should we let him go?

116
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,600
Leave?

117
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,120
Sure.

118
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,600
Then leave an arm behind.

119
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,240
Dailing.

120
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,560
Let him go.

121
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,100
Dailing, why are you here?

122
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,820
Go quickly.

123
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,440
Such deep affection.

124
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,920
In such a hurry to die?

125
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,040
Danpa.

126
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,320
Don't you just want one of my hands?

127
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:14,880
Take it.

128
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:15,920
Let her go.

129
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,400
If you lay a finger on him,

130
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,900
I'll blow his head off.

131
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,280
Look closely.

132
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,930
The situation seems more in our favor now.

133
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,060
Ou Shaowen, what exactly do you want?

134
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,040
What do I want?

135
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,060
Since Dailing is here to save you,

136
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,559
let her be my woman.

137
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,330
Then I'll let you go.

138
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,370
Ou Shaowen, keep dreaming!

139
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,400
Ang Wei!

140
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,559
Ou Shaowen!

141
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:43,820
Ou Shaowen.

142
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,800
Foster father,

143
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,360
what do you think?

144
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,880
Good idea.

145
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,160
Danpa.

146
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,050
What is your choice?

147
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,010
Dailing.

148
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,280
Let him go.

149
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,720
I'll stay.

150
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:10,960
Shaowen,

151
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,120
shouldn't you take action

152
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:15,200
to let Angwei know

153
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,420
that she is your woman?

154
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,040
Ou Shaowen.

155
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:25,600
Ou Shaowen.

156
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,180
Ou Shaowen.

157
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:28,980
Ou Shaowen.

158
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,000
Ou Shaowen.

159
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,880
Ou Shaowen.

160
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,940
If you don't leave,

161
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,800
I'll do her right in front of you.

162
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,920
Just leave!

163
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:54,720
Danpa.

164
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:55,440
Danpa.

165
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,920
Take her away.

166
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,980
Godfather.

167
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,040
The fire is out.

168
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,120
Are you satisfied?
